#: ../../source/vuln/webcache.rst:2
msgid "Web Cache欺骗攻击"
msgstr "Web Cache Deception Attack"

#: ../../source/vuln/webcache.rst:5
msgid "简介"
msgstr "Introduction"

#: ../../source/vuln/webcache.rst:6
msgid "网站通常都会通过如CDN、负载均衡器、或者反向代理来实现Web缓存功能。通过缓存频繁访问的文件，降低服务器响应延迟。"
msgstr "Websites often implement web caching through CDNs, load balancers, or reverse proxies. By caching frequently accessed files, they reduce server response latency."

#: ../../source/vuln/webcache.rst:8
msgid ""
"例如，网站 ``htttp://www.example.com`` 配置了反向代理。对于那些包含用户个人信息的页面，如 "
"``http://www.example.com/home.php`` "
"，由于每个用户返回的内容有所不同，因此这类页面通常是动态生成，并不会在缓存服务器中进行缓存。通常缓存的主要是可公开访问的静态文件，如css文件、js文件、txt文件、图片等等。此外，很多最佳实践类的文章也建议，对于那些能公开访问的静态文件进行缓存，并且忽略HTTP缓存头。"
msgstr "For example, the website ``htttp://www.example.com`` is configured with a reverse proxy. For pages that contain a user's personal information, such as ``http://www.example.com/home.php``, the returned content differs for each user, so these pages are usually generated dynamically and are not cached by the cache server. Cached content is usually publicly accessible static files, such as CSS files, JS files, TXT files, images, and so on. In addition, many best-practice articles also recommend caching publicly accessible static files while ignoring HTTP cache headers."

#: ../../source/vuln/webcache.rst:10
msgid ""
"Web cache攻击类似于RPO相对路径重写攻击，都依赖于浏览器与服务器对URL的解析方式。当访问不存在的URL时，如 "
"``http://www.example.com/home.php/non-existent.css`` "
"，浏览器发送get请求，依赖于使用的技术与配置，服务器返回了页面 ``http://www.example.com/home.php`` "
"的内容，同时URL地址仍然是 ``http://www.example.com/home.php/non-"
"existent.css``，http头的内容也与直接访问 ``http://www.example.com/home.php`` "
"相同，cacheing header、content-type（此处为text/html）也相同。"
msgstr "Web cache attacks are similar to RPO relative path overwrite attacks: both depend on how browsers and servers parse URLs. When a nonexistent URL is accessed, such as ``http://www.example.com/home.php/non-existent.css``, the browser sends a GET request. Depending on the technology and configuration in use, the server may return the content of ``http://www.example.com/home.php`` while the URL remains ``http://www.example.com/home.php/non-existent.css``. The HTTP headers are also the same as those returned by directly accessing ``http://www.example.com/home.php``, including the caching header and content-type, which in this case is text/html."

#: ../../source/vuln/webcache.rst:13
msgid "漏洞成因"
msgstr "Root Cause"

#: ../../source/vuln/webcache.rst:14
msgid ""
"当代理服务器设置为缓存静态文件并忽略这类文件的caching header时，访问 "
"``http://www.example.com/home.php/no-existent.css`` 时，会发生什么呢？整个响应流程如下："
msgstr "When a proxy server is configured to cache static files and ignore caching headers for these files, what happens when ``http://www.example.com/home.php/no-existent.css`` is accessed? The full response flow is as follows:"

#: ../../source/vuln/webcache.rst:16
msgid "浏览器请求 ``http://www.example.com/home.php/no-existent.css`` ;"
msgstr "The browser requests ``http://www.example.com/home.php/no-existent.css``;"

#: ../../source/vuln/webcache.rst:17
msgid "服务器返回 ``http://www.example.com/home.php`` 的内容(通常来说不会缓存该页面);"
msgstr "The server returns the content of ``http://www.example.com/home.php``; normally this page would not be cached."

#: ../../source/vuln/webcache.rst:18
msgid "响应经过代理服务器;"
msgstr "The response passes through the proxy server;"

#: ../../source/vuln/webcache.rst:19
msgid "代理识别该文件有css后缀;"
msgstr "The proxy identifies the file as having a CSS suffix;"

#: ../../source/vuln/webcache.rst:20
msgid "在缓存目录下，代理服务器创建目录 ``home.php`` ，将返回的内容作为 ``non-existent.css`` 保存。"
msgstr "In the cache directory, the proxy server creates the directory ``home.php`` and stores the returned content as ``non-existent.css``."

#: ../../source/vuln/webcache.rst:23
msgid "漏洞利用"
msgstr "Exploitation"

#: ../../source/vuln/webcache.rst:24
msgid ""
"攻击者欺骗用户访问 ``http://www.example.com/home.php/logo.png?www.myhack58.com`` "
",导致含有用户个人信息的页面被缓存，从而能被公开访问到。更严重的情况下，如果返回的内容包含session标识、安全问题的答案，或者csrf "
"token。这样攻击者能接着获得这些信息，因为通常而言大部分网站静态资源都是公开可访问的。"
msgstr "An attacker tricks a user into visiting ``http://www.example.com/home.php/logo.png?www.myhack58.com``, causing a page that contains the user's personal information to be cached and then publicly accessible. In more serious cases, the returned content may include a session identifier, security-question answers, or a CSRF token. The attacker can then obtain this information because static resources on most websites are usually publicly accessible."

#: ../../source/vuln/webcache.rst:27
msgid "漏洞存在的条件"
msgstr "Conditions for the Vulnerability"

#: ../../source/vuln/webcache.rst:28
msgid "漏洞要存在，至少需要满足下面两个条件："
msgstr "For the vulnerability to exist, at least the following two conditions must be met:"

#: ../../source/vuln/webcache.rst:30
msgid "web cache功能根据扩展进行保存，并忽略caching header;"
msgstr "The web cache stores content based on file extension and ignores caching headers;"

#: ../../source/vuln/webcache.rst:31
msgid ""
"当访问如 ``http://www.example.com/home.php/non-existent.css`` 不存在的页面，会返回 "
"``home.php`` 的内容。"
msgstr "When a nonexistent page such as ``http://www.example.com/home.php/non-existent.css`` is accessed, the content of ``home.php`` is returned."

#: ../../source/vuln/webcache.rst:34
msgid "漏洞防御"
msgstr "Mitigation"

#: ../../source/vuln/webcache.rst:35
msgid "防御措施主要包括3点："
msgstr "Mitigations mainly include three points:"

#: ../../source/vuln/webcache.rst:37
msgid "设置缓存机制，仅仅缓存http caching header允许的文件，这能从根本上杜绝该问题;"
msgstr "Configure the caching mechanism to cache only files permitted by HTTP caching headers; this fundamentally prevents the issue;"

#: ../../source/vuln/webcache.rst:38
msgid "如果缓存组件提供选项，设置为根据content-type进行缓存;"
msgstr "If the cache component provides the option, configure it to cache based on content-type;"

#: ../../source/vuln/webcache.rst:39
msgid ""
"访问 ``http://www.example.com/home.php/non-existent.css`` 这类不存在页面，不返回 "
"``home.php`` 的内容，而返回404或者302。"
msgstr "For nonexistent pages such as ``http://www.example.com/home.php/non-existent.css``, return 404 or 302 instead of returning the content of ``home.php``."

